title: Behind the Scenes Minis: Leicester and Dr. Calinda Lee
itunes:title: Behind the Scenes Minis: Leicester and Dr. Calinda Lee
description:
Holly and Tracy discuss the relationship between the Hemingway brothers and the challenges of claiming one's own island. Holly also shares her experiences spending an afternoon at the Atlanta History Center.
